reviewText: Classic Vince Vaughn... the everyman underdog comes through again and again...
Great bundle and at 7.99 it was a great deal
Three great films that make me laugh every time I see them. I truly can identify with Vince Vaughn since I am that all also. Everyone enjoys a good laugh when you are feeling down or always.
Good combo of movies for the price.
Am very happy with it, not a single complaint good price and arrived on time. Would recommend it.
Always like getting 2/ or 3 movie deals.
Nice triple feature for the price! They all worked well.
These guys are fun..What else can one say about these movies.  I thought the price was great and fast shipping.  I like the extra features on the movies
Wicked Awesome! "We were in a blender...and now we're saving lives!!!" lol
For the price of $5, its good to get all 3 movies.  But aside from Dodgeball, the other two are boring and not even funny
